body.openAI_prompt: SYSTEM You will be provided with a tweet, and your task is to classify its sentiment as positive, neutral, or negative. USER I loved the new Batman movie!
body.bedrock_promp: You will be provided with a tweet that you need to analyze and classify the sentiment as positive, neutral, or negative. Here is the tweet: {$TWEET} Carefully read through the tweet and think about the overall sentiment expressed. Is the sentiment positive, neutral, or negative? Provide a justification for your sentiment classification based on the content and tone of the tweet. Write your sentiment classification and justification inside the following tags: [Sentiment Classification]: [Positive/Neutral/Negative] [Justification]: [Provide a 1-2 sentence justification for the sentiment classification]
